<bioghist altrender="history" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
	<head>Historical Note</head>
	<p>The town of Berlin was incorporated in May 1785 and was taken from Farmington, Wethersfield and Middletown. New Britain separated from Berlin in May 1850.</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
	<head>Scope and Content</head>
	<p>Tax, election and Borough of Worthington meeting records for the town of Berlin.
</p>
</scopecontent>

